Parents, friends and supporters;

We have created a new online registration link for families who want to learn more about our great Academy. We need to test this just a little bit, so please click on this and fill it out, and give us feedback. Once we have this polished we will start sending it out on social media. You can also forward this to any of your friends who you think might want to enroll their child. Great things are happening! We are excited about next year.

